{"word":"Jezebel","slug":"jezebel","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Jezebel</b> <a href=\"#/H348\">H348</a> <br/> Daughter of Ethbaal, a Zidonian, and wife of Ahab<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=31'>1Ki 16:31</a><br/> Was an idolatress and persecuted the prophets of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=18&verse=4'>1Ki 18:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=18&verse=13'>1Ki 18:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=18&verse=19'>1Ki 18:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=3&verse=2'>2Ki 3:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=3&verse=13'>2Ki 3:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=7'>2Ki 9:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=22'>2Ki 9:22</a><br/> Vowed to kill Elijah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=3'>1Ki 19:3</a><br/> Wickedly accomplishes the death of Naboth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=16'>1Ki 21:16</a><br/> Death of, foretold<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=23'>1Ki 21:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=10'>2Ki 9:10</a><br/> Death of, at the hand of Jehu<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=37'>2Ki 9:37</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=2&verse=20'>Rev 2:20</a>"}]}